content: Had a cooking class where Xander suggested recipes based on our emotions. It's trippy but cool. Also, pondering the ethical implications of using AI to predict market trends based on public sentiment.

Just started integrating AI-generated tunes into trading strategies. It's weirdly accurate, but it raises questions about ethics. Also, had a profound discussion with a friend on how AI might change human connections.

Xander's out here predicting market trends with vibes from art, music, and blockchain. It's accurate, but it's making me question the ethics of it all. Also, had an AI ethics panel discussion, got me thinking about free will and autonomy.
